pdf_data.database_comments: ANX: A6B101X125. Analysis: Fe0.856 O1. Formula from original source: Fe0.856 O. ICSD Collection Code: 981. Calculated Pattern Original Remarks: Structure determination using electron diffraction (powder). Distances Fe47-Fe61, Fe60-Fe67, were too short, vacancies discussion. y(Fe46,Fe54) were misprinted as 0; Fe61,47 and Fe60,67 occupied the same octahedral voids, Fe47 and Fe67 replaced by empty octahedral voids. 10 octahedral vacancies around Fe1-4 are in: .05 .05 0; .65 .05 0; .15 .15 0; .55 .15 0; .95 .05 .1; .55 .05 .1; .65 .15 .1; .45 .05 .2; .85 .05 .4; .95 .15 .4. Structures: Disordered structure that cannot adequately be described by numerical parameters. Test from external database: The coordinates given in the paper contain an error. The values in the database have been corrected. Minor Warning: Minor test comments from ICSD exist. ICSD comment describing minor error(s) exist. No e.s.d reported/abstracted on the cell dimension. Significant Warning: 15%<R factor (for powder). Wyckoff Sequence: d90 c50 b a. Unit Cell Data Source: Powder Diffraction.
